
'''''Rimwe na rimwe muri Mata''''' ni filime y'akozwe n'abany[[amerika]] muri 2005 ivuga kuri [[Itsembabwoko ry’u Rwanda ry’1994|jenoside]] yakorewe Abatutsi mu 1994 mu [[Rwanda]] , yanditswe kandi iyobowe n'umukinnyi wa filime wo [[Hayiti|muri Hayiti]] Raoul Peck. Abakinnyi bagize itsinda barimo Idris Elba, Oris Erhuero, Carole Karemera, na Debra Winger .

== Uko yateguwe ==
Bitandukanye na ''[[Hotel Rwanda]]'', yahawe igihembo cya PG-13 kandi ikaba yaravugaga mu buryo bwihishe inyuma ya jenoside aho kwerekana ku buryo bweruye, iyi filime yari izwiho kwerekana ihohoterwa rishingiye ku gitsina, ryayihaye TV-MA. Byongeye kandi, amashusho atandukanye yashyizwe mu Rwanda yafatiwe muri Kigali no hafi yayo, hagaragaramo ahantu nyaburanga nka Hotel des Mille Collines ndetse na kiliziya [[Kiriziya y'umuryango mutagatifu|ya Sainte-Famille]] .

Filime yabanje kwerekanwa kuri HBO . Nyuma yaje gutangazwa na PBS hanyuma isesengurwa  n’umunyamakuru jeff Greenfield hamwe na Paul Bonerwitz hamwe n’abandi .
